{"tid":648724,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"墾丁大街成全台最爛夜市","createTime":"2018-05-01T02:45:29.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-01T08:53:15.000Z","uid":25558,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"14cbd7f5d98d41bb89d1c8d7f9033c0af705ee2e","tid":648724,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-01T02:45:29.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180501/20377919?_ga=2.141134770.1029761066.1520127978-1555213041.1517019171\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180501%2F20377919%3F_ga%3D2.141134770.1029761066.1520127978-1555213041.1517019171&d=uWXdQhWoVnubLJeAKiDwLpZgE6vMW1KEzMhkvokIvkY%3D&h=0377a27b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180501%2F20377919%3F_ga%3D2.141134770.1029761066.1520127978-1555213041.1517019171&h=91825212\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180501/20377919?_ga=2.141134770.1029761066.1520127978-1555213041.1517019171</a><br />\n<br />\n2018年05月01日 <br />\n<br />\n墾丁大街成全台最爛夜市<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20180501/large/a0503a.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20180501%2Flarge%2Fa0503a.gif&h=553a5d49&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n墾丁大街夜市<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】台灣夜巿劏客事件時有發生，日前台灣傳媒公佈「全台最爛夜市」的投票結果，三甲位置分別是墾丁大街、高雄六合夜巿及台北士林夜巿，至於票數最低的則是台中逢甲夜巿，僅獲45票，「負皮」最少。<br />\n <br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20180501/large/a0503b.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20180501%2Flarge%2Fa0503b.gif&h=dbb55aaa&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n標價不實　衞生差<br />\n<br />\n台灣網站《yamNews》早前邀請網民投票，選出「全台最爛夜市」，共1,248人參加，其中墾丁大街以266票佔據榜首，得票率21%，而高雄六合夜市則以238票緊隨其後，得票率19%，雙雙以大比數拋離排第三的台北士林夜巿。各夜市的問題主要為店舖標價不實、不正當抬價、衞生環境差等。<br />\n<br />\n墾丁大街一名姓蔡商人表示，去年增設垃圾桶及清潔工人打掃後，衞生問題已有改善。<br />\n墾丁大街自治管委會主委曾春惠無奈地說，現在攤販只能互相鼓勵，下月春浪音樂節將重返墾丁，希望藉此重振形象。<br />\n<br />\n至於亞軍的六合夜市，有水果店坦言對投票結果感到難過，自言是30多年的老店，一直都是明碼實價，提醒消費者在夜市購買水果前可先請商人秤重。六合觀光夜市發展促進會主委莊其章則批評網民不公平，指夜巿有許多價廉物美的小食，一直沒加價。<br />\n<br />\n墾丁大街近年屢傳劏客事件，當地的滷味、乾麵及漢堡因商人開天索價，被網民戲稱為「墾丁三寶」，令旅遊業重創，自2016年開始，墾丁觀光人次大跌211萬人，被形容為雪崩式下跌。  <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n英護膚品牌　于品海14億收購<br />\n<br />\n下一則<br />\n《爆相爆片》四月第三輪揭曉<br />\n<br />\n英護膚品牌　于品海14億收購<br />\n<br />\nCrabtree ＆ Evelyn懷孕員工　被炒兩次　遭警押走不滿受歧視　入稟獲賠10萬"},{"pid":"63fe37178d354b3d36c4b4502436db1f645e5c67","tid":648724,"uid":57376,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-01T02:47:47.000Z","msg":"中國人做生意係咁架啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7ada08f21ee21d331901654d0fc49ea622243929","tid":648724,"uid":57555,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-01T02:49:34.000Z","msg":"抵死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不詔被拖累、正經做生意果D好慘"},{"pid":"ad85bbcacb8b30df94dc234063fdc723c8193302","tid":648724,"uid":57555,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-01T02:49:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>抵死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不<span style=\"color: red;\">過</span>被拖累、正經做生意果D好慘</blockquote>"},{"pid":"2fec671321a641f76b096be8ed88cde3f8f50f64","tid":648724,"uid":1646,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-01T02:52:37.000Z","msg":"當人on9係咁劏<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7ff281c5e7e64507a30642a39760e68d7569e2b9","tid":648724,"uid":55800,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-01T02:54:21.000Z","msg":"羅東夜市真心唔錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /